 If you want the accuracy of angles to be 1 degree, you need 180 columns. For œÅ, the maximum distance possible is the diagonal length of the image.

int maxTheta = 180;
int houghHeight = (int)( Math.Sqrt( 2 ) * Math.Max( imgWidth, imgHeight ) ) / 2;
int doubleHoughHeight = houghHeight * 2;